1. *Telefona* je odlična stvar za komunikaciju. (The phone is a great thing for communication.)
2. *Telefonirala* sam svojoj sestri pre nego što sam pošla u školu. (I phoned my sister before I went to school.)
3. Moje dete stalno gleda u *telefon*. (My child is always looking at the phone.)
4. On je obrisao sve fotografije sa *telefona*. (He deleted all the photos from the phone.)
5. To je bio prvi *telefon* koji je imao kameru. (It was the first phone that had a camera.)